#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Using VeraCrypt encrypted volumes\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Verwendung von VeraCrypt-verschlüsselten Volumen\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!toc levels=2]]\n"
msgstr "[[!toc levels=2]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Introduction to *VeraCrypt*\n"
"==========================================================\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*[VeraCrypt](https://www.veracrypt.fr/)* is a\n"
"disk encryption tool that works on Windows, macOS, and Linux.\n"
msgstr ""
"*[VeraCrypt](https://www.veracrypt.fr/)* ist ein\n"
"Festplattenverschlüsselungsprogramm, das unter Windows, macOS und Linux funktioniert.\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Comparison between *LUKS* and *VeraCrypt*"
msgstr "Vergleich zwischen *LUKS* und *VeraCrypt*"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"You can also create and open *LUKS* encrypted volumes in Tails. *LUKS* is "
"the standard for disk encryption in Linux. [[See our documentation about "
"*LUKS*.|encrypted_volumes]]"
msgstr ""
"Sie können auch *LUKS*-verschlüsselte Volumes in Tails erstellen und öffnen. "
"*LUKS* ist der  Standard für die Festplattenverschlüsselung unter Linux. "
"[[Siehe unsere Dokumentation zu *LUKS*.|encrypted_volumes]]"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!inline pages=\"doc/encryption_and_privacy/luks_vs_veracrypt.inline\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!inline pages=\"doc/encryption_and_privacy/luks_vs_veracrypt.inline.de\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<div class=\"next\">\n"
msgstr "<div class=\"next\">\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<p>To create new <i>VeraCrypt</i> volumes, do so outside of Tails. See\n"
"[[VeraCrypt: Beginner's Tutorial|https://veracrypt.io/en/Beginner%27s%20Tutorial.html]].</p>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "</div>\n"
msgstr "</div>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<a id=\"container-vs-partition\"></a>\n"
msgstr "<a id=\"container-vs-partition\"></a>\n"

#. type: Title -
#, no-wrap
msgid "Difference between file containers and partitions"
msgstr "Unterschied zwischen Dateicontainern und Partitionen"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"With *VeraCrypt* you can store your files encrypted in two different kinds "
"of *volumes*:"
msgstr ""
"Mit *VeraCrypt* können Sie Ihre Dateien  in zwei verschiedenen Arten von "
"*Volumes* verschlüsselt speichern:"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<h3>File containers</h3>\n"
msgstr "<h3>Dateicontainer</h3>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<div class=\"icon\">\n"
msgstr "<div class=\"icon\">\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!img container-icon.png link=\"no\" alt=\"\"]]\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<div class=\"text\">\n"
"<p>A file container is a single big file inside which you can store\n"
"several files encrypted, a bit like a ZIP file.</p>\n"
"</div>\n"
"</div>\n"
msgstr ""
"<div class=\"text\">\n"
"<p>Ein Dateicontainer ist eine einzelne große Datei, in der Sie mehrere verschlüsselte Dateien speichern können, ähnlich wie bei einer ZIP-Datei.</p>\n"
"</div>\n"
"</div>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<h3>Partitions or drives</h3>\n"
msgstr "<h3>Partitionen oder Laufwerke</h3>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!img partition-icon.png link=\"no\" alt=\"\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!img partition-icon.png link=\"no\" alt=\"\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<div class=\"text\">\n"
"<p>Usually, drives (USB sticks and hard disks) have a single partition of their\n"
"entire size. This way, you can encrypt a whole USB stick, for example.\n"
"But, drives can also be split into several partitions.\n"
"</div>\n"
"</div>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<a id=\"parameters\"></a>\n"
msgstr "<a id=\"parameters\"></a>\n"

#. type: Title -
#, no-wrap
msgid "Unlocking parameters"
msgstr "Entsperrparameter"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To unlock a *VeraCrypt* volume, you might need the following parameters, "
"depending on the options that were selected when the volume was created:"
msgstr ""
"Um ein *VeraCrypt*-Volume zu entsperren, benötigen Sie möglicherweise die "
"folgenden Parameter, abhängig von den Optionen, die bei der Erstellung des "
"Volumes ausgewählt wurden:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "- **Passphrase**"
msgid "**Passphrase**"
msgstr "- **Passwortphrase**"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"**Keyfiles**: instead of or in addition to the passphrase, a *VeraCrypt* "
"volume can be unlocked using a particular file or set of files."
msgstr ""
"**Schlüsseldateien**: Anstelle von oder zusätzlich zur Passwortphrase kann "
"ein *VeraCrypt*-Volume mit einer bestimmten Datei oder einer Gruppe von "
"Dateien entsperrt werden."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  [See the *VeraCrypt* documentation on\n"
"  keyfiles.](https://www.veracrypt.fr/en/Keyfiles.html)\n"
msgstr ""
"  [Siehe die *VeraCrypt*-Dokumentation\n"
"  zu Schlüsseldateien.](https://www.veracrypt.fr/en/Keyfiles.html)\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"**PIM**: a number that is needed if it was specified when creating the "
"*VeraCrypt* volume."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  [See the *VeraCrypt* documentation on\n"
"  PIM.](https://www.veracrypt.fr/en/Personal%20Iterations%20Multiplier%20\\(PIM\\).html)\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"**Hidden volume**: if you want to unlock the hidden volume inside the "
"*VeraCrypt* volume."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  [See the *VeraCrypt* documentation on hidden\n"
"  volumes.](https://www.veracrypt.fr/en/Hidden%20Volume.html)\n"
msgstr ""
"  [Siehe die *VeraCrypt*-Dokumentation zu versteckten\n"
"  Volumes.](https://www.veracrypt.fr/en/Hidden%20Volume.html)\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"**System volume**: if you want to unlock an encrypted Windows system "
"partition."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  [See the *VeraCrypt* documentation on\n"
"  encrypting a Windows system partition.](https://www.veracrypt.fr/en/System%20Encryption.html)\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using a file container"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<a id=\"container-files\"></a>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title -
#, no-wrap
msgid "Unlocking a file container without keyfiles"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Choose **Applications&nbsp;▸ Utilities&nbsp;▸ Unlock VeraCrypt Volumes**."
msgid "Choose **Apps&nbsp;▸ Utilities&nbsp;▸ Unlock VeraCrypt Volumes**."
msgstr ""
"Wählen Sie **Anwendungen**&nbsp;▸ **Dienstprogramme**&nbsp;▸ **Festplatten** "
"aus, um das *Festplatten*-Dienstprogramm zu starten."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Click **Add** and choose the file container that you want to unlock."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Enter the parameters to unlock the volume. For more information, see the "
"[[Unlocking parameters|veracrypt#parameters]] section above."
msgstr ""
"Geben Sie die Parameter ein, um das Volume zu entsperren. Weitere "
"Informationen finden Sie im Abschnitt [[Entsperrparameter|"
"veracrypt#parameters]] weiter oben."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Click **Unlock**."
msgstr "Klicken Sie auf **Entsperren**."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   *Unlock VeraCrypt Volumes* unlocks your volume.\n"
msgstr "   *VeraCrypt-Container entsperren* entsperrt Ihr Volume.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   If unlocking the volume fails (for example, if you mistyped the\n"
"   password), click on **Unlock** to try\n"
"   unlocking again.\n"
msgstr "   Wenn das Entsperren des Volumes fehlschlägt (zum Beispiel, wenn Sie das Passwort falsch eingegeben haben), klicken Sie auf **Entsperren**, um es erneut zu versuchen.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Click **Open** to open the volume in the *Files* browser."
msgstr ""
"Klicken Sie auf **Öffnen**, um das Volumen im <span "
"class=\"application\">Dateien</span>-Browser zu öffnen."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<a id=\"container-disks\"></a>\n"
msgstr "<a id=\"container-disks\"></a>\n"

#. type: Title -
#, no-wrap
msgid "Unlocking a file container with keyfiles"
msgstr "Entsperren eines Datei-Containers mit Schlüsseldateien"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Choose **Applications&nbsp;▸ Utilities&nbsp;▸ Disks** to start the "
#| "*Disks* utility."
msgid ""
"Choose **Apps&nbsp;▸ Utilities&nbsp;▸ Disks** to open the *Disks* utility."
msgstr ""
"Wählen Sie **Anwendungen**&nbsp;▸ **Dienstprogramme**&nbsp;▸ **Festplatten** "
"aus, um das *Festplatten*-Dienstprogramm zu starten."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Choose **[[!img lib/open-menu.png alt=\"\" class=symbolic "
#| "link=\"no\"]]&nbsp;▸ Attach Disk Image&hellip;** from the top navigation "
#| "bar."
msgid ""
"Choose **[[!img lib/open-menu.png link=\"no\" class=\"symbolic\" "
"alt=\"\"]]&nbsp;▸ Attach Disk Image** from the top navigation bar."
msgstr ""
"Wählen Sie **[[!img lib/open-menu.png alt=\"\" class=symbolic "
"link=\"no\"]]&nbsp;▸ Festplattendatei anhängen&hellip;** aus der oberen "
"Navigationsleiste."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "In the **Select Disk Image to Attach** dialog:"
msgstr ""
"Im <span class=\"bold\">Dialog \"Disk-Image Auswählen, um es anzuhängen\"</"
"span>:"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
msgid ""
"Unselect the **Set up read-only loop device** check box in the bottom-left "
"corner if you want to modify the content of the file container."
msgstr ""
"Deaktivieren Sie das Kontrollkästchen <span "
"class=\"guilabel\">Schreibgeschütztes Loop-Gerät einrichten</span> in der "
"unteren linken Ecke, wenn Sie den Inhalt des Dateicontainers ändern möchten."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "     [[!img read-only.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"\"]]\n"
msgstr "     [[!img read-only.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"\"]]\n"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
msgid "Choose **All Files** in the file filter in the bottom-right corner."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "     [[!img all-files.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"\"]]\n"
msgstr "     [[!img all-files.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"\"]]\n"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
msgid ""
"Navigate to the folder containing the file container that you want to open."
msgstr ""
"Navigieren Sie zu dem Ordner, der den Dateicontainer enthält, den Sie öffnen "
"möchten."

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
msgid "Select the file container and click **Attach**."
msgstr ""
"Wählen Sie den Dateicontainer aus und klicken Sie auf <span "
"class=\"bold\">Anhängen</span>."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "A first dialog appears to unlock the container."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "     [[!img read-only.png link=\"no\" class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"\"]]\n"
msgid "   [[!img authentication.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"Authentication required\"]]\n"
msgstr "     [[!img read-only.png link=\"no\" class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"\"]]\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Select **Cancel**."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   It is impossible to use keyfiles with this first dialog.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"A second dialog called **Set options to unlock** appears to unlock the "
"container."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   [[!img options.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"\"]]\n"
msgstr "   [[!img options.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"\"]]\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Open your *VeraCrypt* volume from the sidebar of the *Files* menu."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using a partition or drive"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<h2 id=\"partition-external\">Unlocking a partition on an external storage device</h2>\n"
msgstr "<h2 id=\"partition-external\">Entsperren einer Partition auf einem externen Speichergerät</h2>\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Plug in the USB stick or hard disk that you want to unlock."
msgstr ""
"Stecken Sie den USB-Stick oder die Festplatte ein, die Sie entsperren "
"möchten."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   An authentication dialog appears.\n"
msgstr "   Ein Authentifizierungsdialog erscheint.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<h2 id=\"partition-internal\">Unlocking a partition on an internal hard disk</h2>\n"
msgstr "<h2 id=\"partition-internal\">Eine Partition auf einer internen Festplatte entsperren</h2>\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"When starting Tails, [[set up an administration password|doc/first_steps/"
"welcome_screen/administration_password]]."
msgstr ""
"Beim Starten von Tails [[richten Sie ein Administrationspasswort ein|doc/"
"first_steps/welcome_screen/administration_password]]."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "In the left pane, select the drive that corresponds to your hard disk."
msgstr ""
"Wählen Sie im linken Bereich das Laufwerk aus, das Ihrer Festplatte "
"entspricht."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"In the right pane, select the partition that corresponds to your *VeraCrypt* "
"volume."
msgstr ""
"Wählen Sie im rechten Bereich die Partition aus, die Ihrem *VeraCrypt*-"
"Volume entspricht."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   It should have an **Encrypted?** label.\n"
msgstr "   Es sollte ein **Verschlüsselt?**-Label haben.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Click the [[!img lib/unlock.png alt=\"Unlock selected encrypted partition\" "
"class=\"symbolic\" link=\"no\"]] button in the right pane."
msgstr ""
"Klicken Sie auf die [[!img lib/unlock.png alt=\"Ausgewählte verschlüsselte "
"Partition entsperren\" class=\"symbolic\" link=\"no\"]] Schaltfläche im "
"rechten Bereich."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Select the file system that appears below the unlocked volume."
msgstr ""
"Wählen Sie das Dateisystem aus, das unter dem entsperrten Volume angezeigt "
"wird."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Click the [[!img lib/media-playback-start.png alt=\"Mount selected "
"partition\" class=\"symbolic\" link=\"no\"]] button to mount the volume."
msgstr ""
"Klicken Sie auf die [[!img lib/media-playback-start.png alt=\"Ausgewählte "
"Partition einbinden\" class=\"symbolic\" link=\"no\"]] Schaltfläche, um das "
"Volume einzubinden."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Click on the */media/amnesia/* link in the right pane to open the volume in "
"the *Files* browser."
msgstr ""
"Klicken Sie im rechten Bereich auf den */media/amnesia/*-Link, um das Volume "
"im *Dateien*-Browser zu öffnen."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<h2 id=\"eject\">Ejecting a <i>VeraCrypt</i> volume</h2>\n"
msgstr "<h2 id=\"eject\">Auswerfen eines <i>VeraCrypt</i>-Volumes</h2>\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Choose **Applications**&nbsp;▸ **Files** to open the *Files* browser."
msgid ""
"Choose **Apps&nbsp;▸ Accessories&nbsp;▸ Files** to open the *Files* browser."
msgstr ""
"Wählen Sie **Anwendungen**&nbsp;▸ **Dateien**, um den *Dateien*-Browser zu "
"öffnen."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"In the sidebar of the *Files* browser, click on the [[!img lib/media-"
"eject.png alt=\"Eject\" class=\"symbolic\" link=\"no\"]] button on the label "
"of your *VeraCrypt* volume."
msgstr ""
"Klicken Sie in der Seitenleiste des *Dateien*-Browsers auf die [[!img lib/"
"media-eject.png alt=\"Auswerfen\" class=\"symbolic\" link=\"no\"]] "
"Schaltfläche auf dem Label Ihres *VeraCrypt*-Volumes."

